lead_paragraph: The Los Angeles Lakers have the NBA's highest-scoring bench and remarkable balance throughout their roster, as the Atlanta Hawks discovered for the second time this month.

headline.print_headline: Lou Williams Leads Lakers to Season Sweep of Hawks, 109-94
